<p><img src="../images/award.jpg" alt="excellence award"/><h1>VOTED #1 again!</h1>
<p>20th July, 2014</p>
<p>SKWAllArt has been voted the <span class="bold"> no.1 web design company in Yorkshire</span> in the<span class="bold"> Times
Annual Web Design Survey 2014</span>. The overall ranking was inclusive of individual 
ranking across  several important parameters of good web design including appearance,
functionality, website usability and search engine optimisation.
<p> We're immensely grateful for the continued faith that our clients show in us.
SKWallArt has been voted no.1 in Yorkshire for the<span class="bold"> third consecutive year</span> and we intend to continue this trend in the coming years.</p>
</article>
