<!--third article-->
<article id="article">
<h1>YORKSHIRE TRIBUNE: June 5, 2013</h1>
<p>
<span class="bold">"Truly elegant design incorporates top-notch functionality into a simple uncluttered form".</span> 
In a press conference held yesterday at Hotel Grand Central, London, the 'Global Interactive Media Forum' announced the names of the 3 recipients of GIMBA June 2013.  It was a proud moment for Yorkshire that SKWallArt was chosen for the Best Design in the Web Designing Section.

SKWallArt's revolutionary design for the National Health Organisation's online portal has been in the news since its launch earlier this year owing to its elegance and transparency. Since its inception in year 2003, SKWallArt has rapidly risen to become the undisputed leader of the web designers' community in the U.K. Now with the prestigious GIMBA,
SKWallArt wins global recognition as a quality designer.
</p>
</article>
